{"tid":2098938,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求相! Cosplay女生亂入動漫展無著內褲掀裙露下體任影警介入調查","createTime":"2020-07-08T00:55:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T02:59:54.000Z","uid":141892,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0556487ad9bb3fbb2270c9edb3d921d9f36292d4","tid":2098938,"uid":141892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00:55:23.000Z","msg":"很多Cosplay愛好者喜歡扮演不同的動漫角色，但不代表可以藉此賣弄色情。台灣日前舉行一連兩日的「PF（Petit Fancy）32亞洲動漫創作展」，1名女Coser竟當眾掀起裙子讓圍觀的人們任影任看，更嚴重的是原來她沒有穿內褲，事件引來社會關注。<br />\n<br />\n警方事後介入調查，涉事女子今日（6日）下午已到圓山派出所接受調查，其所屬大學則表示遺憾和抱歉，稱女生「身心有點狀況」正在休學，將按校規處理事件。展覽主辦單位對事件感到遺憾，強調對Cosplay參與者的服裝規定有作宣導規勸與管制，並表示會配合警方調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/b57961/f/800x0/https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200706/356803189057654784.jpeg/k394dTAyVveeNwolL5cLT0OtR8NYE8MILz4Vxy8-Fcc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2Fb57961%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200706%2F356803189057654784.jpeg%2Fk394dTAyVveeNwolL5cLT0OtR8NYE8MILz4Vxy8-Fcc&h=90ad7e79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3cee1deeeb83b1a86c067a0c9b1ed905e0fa44c","tid":2098938,"uid":18465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00:58:28.000Z","msg":"髒東西在哪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98fd9cc634ecef86cc80cd5c2e6c1aa05ee12aaf","tid":2098938,"uid":356101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3cee1deeeb83b1a86c067a0c9b1ed905e0fa44c","tid":2098938,"uid":18465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00:58:28.000Z","msg":"髒東西在哪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:00:08.000Z","msg":"比叔叔睇下有幾髒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da507baa3f35e0ad86e6a5d959dd5bcf3ec56196","tid":2098938,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"沒圖 打